`key` needs `NOT NULL` constraint to prevent nulls (primary key isn't enough).

```
$ sqlite3
SQLite version 3.30.1 2019-10-10 20:19:45
sqlite> CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS main(key BLOB PRIMARY KEY, value BLOB NOT NULL);
sqlite> insert into main values (null, 'value');
sqlite> select * from main;
|value
